Sept 10 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Wednesday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

NORTHLAND CAPITAL PARTNERS LTD The London-based investment bank said it appointed Patrick Claridge its chief executive with immediate effect. [ID:nL3N0RB3BZ]  VTB CAPITAL [VTBCA.UL]  Damian Chunilal has resigned as Asia CEO of the bank after more than two years as the Russian investment bank's top executive in the region. [ID:nL3N0RB38U]  MIZUHO SECURITIES ASIA LTD The company said it appointed Scott Paul as managing director and head of Pan Asian fixed income sales in Hong Kong. [ID:nL3N0RB2I4]   AVIVA ASIA